      <persName role="Press Photographer Vreme"><forename>Svetozar </forename><surname>Grdijan</surname><ref type="context" target="info:fedora/context:siba.pn.d2666bab">Grdijan, Svetozar </ref><certainty target="persName" cert="medium" locus="value" /></persName></ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">A group of seven smartly dressed men sitting around a small round table on a terrace in the open. One of them, with bowler hat and cigarette, is talking to an eighth man who is standing next to the table, holding a violin and laughing into the camera. His equally elegant dress suggests he belongs to the group. On the table are eight glasses, a jug of red wine, a soda bottle and a plate of cakes. Another male party in the background consists of men in uniform. It is a sunny day in spring or autumn, since some of the men wear their coats. The hills around Belgrade are seen in the background.</ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet" subtype="comment">Probably <ref target="http://gams.uni-graz.at/o:siba.glossar?mode=K5">kafana</ref> 'Dedinje' on Prince Aleksandar Boulevard.</ab>
